data.name: Team Aqua's Sharpedo
rules: This Pokémon is both Water Darkness type.

attacks.name: Rage
attacks.text: Does 10 damage plus 10 more damage for each damage counter on Team Aqua's Sharpedo.

attacks.name: Aqua Slash
attacks.text: Team Aqua's Sharpedo can't attack during your next turn.

attacks.name: Aqua Jet

data.flavorText: It drinks in seawater and jets it from its rear to propel itself. It's very sensitive to the scent of blood.

data.name: Sharpedo
data.flavorText: It pursues its prey at speeds of 75 mph and finishes them off with fangs that can crush iron. It is known as the bully of the sea.
